      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The eastern lines have decided\nnot to renew the anti-pass agree\nment. This announcement will be\nreceived with much good feeling\namong the railway men.\n\n\nSuperintendent Long of the Kalis-\npell division is in the city.\n\n\nSuperintendent W. d. Scott of\nthe Everett division is ell route to\nSpokane.\n\n\nThe eastbound Northern Pacific\ntrains were badly delayed today.\n\n\nj. c. Pond of the Wisconsin Cen\ntrail line is touring the west."
    }
